Summary: F-16 sighting followed by brief UFO sighting.
divs: Sighting DetailsI was at work and we had been moving things to storage, my coe-workers were inside and I was outside near the back door where there is a great view of Buffalo Mountain. At this time I saw a jet that looked like an F-16 fly unusually low from Vail towards Frisco, it then took a large turn northward around Buffalo Mountain and toward the Gore Range and I lost sight of it. Right after that I noticed a silver circular object that was hovering behind the southern side of Buffalo Mountain. I had been watching the sky that day and this object was much lower than any of the jets I had observed, besides the F-16. The whole event from the time I saw the F-16 to when the ufo left was around 30 seconds.
